-----------------------------------------------------------------------
  This archive contains 'tcdev', the Makefile-based versions of
software in the STUBS project's Configurations releases. Please note
that the STUBS Toolchain and Utility Build Suite has a web page at:
	http://www.angelfire.com/linux/wills/stubs.html
